Metafrash:
To programma metafrazetai me thn xrhsh enos Makefile to opoio
kanei compile kai linking tou programmatos kai allwn 2 voithitikwn
programmatwn pou xrhsimopoioyntai gia thn dhmiourgia arxeiwn me 
integers kai gia ton elegxo tou arxeiou gia to an einai taksinomimeno.

Dokimh:
To programma dokimazetai mesw tou run_test.sh to opoio xrhsimopoiei ta voitihika
programmata gia na dhmiourghsei ta test inputs kai na elegxei thn orthothta tou
programmatos. Yparxoun 3 epiloges:
1. Arxeio me 1000 unsorted integers
2. Arxeio me 10000 unsorted integers
3. Arxeio me 100000 unsorted integers